
abstract_prop p(x, y)

by transitive_prop:
    prove:
        forall x, y, z set:
            $p(x, y)
            $p(y, z)
            =>:
                $p(x, z)
    know $p(x, z)

have a, b, c set

claim:
    prove:
        $p(a, c)
    know a $p b $p c

# After p is registered as transitive, a $p b $p c stores $p(a, c).